		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=Kogabar&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>I was thinking about making a Rogue, and was justwondering what they where like and if the other pure melee classes are better. And I play in a PvP teams and my friend is going to PL me and buy me stuff tomorrow or today. And is a Cat a good race for a rogue? I play a halfing Ranger right now.<br><br><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sat Oct 23 08:18:59 2004 by Kogabar</span class="sm"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >5 Replies</td></tr></table>
